DeepSeek-V4 NVFP4 (PR #25820) patch-application step for
container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly.

Adds one COPY+RUN step that applies sglang-dsv4-nvfp4-pr25820.patch
(upstream PR #25820 rebased onto v0.5.13 — hybrid FP8+NVFP4 checkpoint
support for nvidia/DeepSeek-V4-Flash-NVFP4) to the sglang Python source
AFTER the SM121 sgl-kernel patches but BEFORE `uv pip install ./python`,
so the installed package picks up the changes. Same pattern as
dockerfile-gemma4-nvfp4.patch.

Apply to: container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly AFTER
dockerfile-sm121.patch has been applied. Application is gated by
build_sm121_image.sh on the recipe variable APPLY_DSV4_NVFP4_PR25820=1
(set in sglang-0.5.13-sm121.recipe; remove the variable / set 0 once
PR #25820 is merged into the pinned SGLANG_REF).

NOTE: anchors on the same Dockerfile region as dockerfile-gemma4-nvfp4
.patch (the end of the sm121-debug block). The two are not used together
today (no gemma4+dsv4 recipe); if that ever changes, apply gemma4 first
and regenerate this patch's context.

--- a/container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly
+++ b/container-build/Dockerfile.sglang-nightly
@@ -290,6 +290,22 @@
         echo "=== Skipping sgl-kernel-sm121-debug.patch (APPLY_SGL_KERNEL_SM121_DEBUG=${APPLY_SGL_KERNEL_SM121_DEBUG}) ==="; \
     fi
 
+# DeepSeek-V4 NVFP4 MoE support (upstream PR #25820, not yet merged).
+# Regenerated against tag v0.5.13 — adds HybridFp8NvFp4Config so hybrid
+# FP8(base)+NVFP4(experts) checkpoints (nvidia/DeepSeek-V4-Flash-NVFP4)
+# load; FusedMoE routes through ModelOptNvFp4FusedMoEMethod. Applied to
+# the sglang Python source before pip install so the installed
+# dist-packages picks up the changes. This COPY+RUN step only exists in
+# builds whose recipe sets APPLY_DSV4_NVFP4_PR25820=1 (the dockerfile
+# patch adding this step is gated by build_sm121_image.sh).
+COPY patches/sglang-dsv4-nvfp4-pr25820.patch /tmp/sglang-dsv4-nvfp4-pr25820.patch
+RUN set -e; cd /data/sglang && \
+    echo "=== Applying sglang-dsv4-nvfp4-pr25820.patch (PR #25820) ===" && \
+    patch --dry-run -p1 < /tmp/sglang-dsv4-nvfp4-pr25820.patch && \
+    patch -p1 < /tmp/sglang-dsv4-nvfp4-pr25820.patch && \
+    grep -q 'HybridFp8NvFp4Config' python/sglang/srt/layers/quantization/modelopt_quant.py && \
+    echo 'DSV4 NVFP4 PR #25820 patch applied successfully'
+
 # Install sglang package (no deps, no build isolation since base has torch).
 # Moved here from its original early-stage location so the installed
 # dist-packages picks up the patched nvfp4_blockwise_moe.cuh above.
